    <h1>üè• Patient UID Migration Tool</h1>
    <p>This tool will update your Supabase organizations table to add clinic codes for patient UID generation.</p>

    <div>
      <strong>UID Format:</strong> <code>CLINICCODE-YYYYMM-XXXX</code><br>
      <strong>Example:</strong> <code>HOPE-202502-0012</code>
